		<div class="row" id="why-switch">
			<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
				<h2>Why do customers Switch?</h2>
				<p>There are a lot of reasons for a switch. Exploring why someone switches is an entire topic onto itself. But to give an idea, here are some examples of why someone does a switch:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>They found a product which does the Job better: Maybe they found a better tasting pizza.</li>
					<li>After doing the job more, they learned more about the Job and their consideration set grew: They learned that they can buy pre-made sushi and can use that instead of pizza.</li>
					<li>The Job changed a little bit: Someone may decide that Pizza on a regular basis is too unhealthy, so they deicded that the Job is not just to solve their hunger in a quick, easy way...but now they want it to be healthy too.</li>
				</ul>
